    "In the \"Results\" section, we cover the experimental setup of benchmark datasets, present their respective results, and discuss the outcomes.",
    "Lastly, the \"Conclusion\" section concludes the paper and explores future directions.",
    "Structured data, such as tables and databases, have a consistent layout and predictable pattern.",
    "In contrast, unstructured data such as written and spoken text lacks a predefined structure, making it difficult to process [25].",
    "These data can consist of diverse languages, and contain grammatical errors, abbreviations, and context-dependent meanings."
  ]
